racters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"我原本還不是正式的團員。\n拍音樂錄影帶的時候終於被認可了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event117-10-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"明日香","body":"的確是非常帥氣呢。\n姊姊他們，也說要參考那個來製作MV呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event117-10-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"欸～Popipa也要嗎！　那我一定要看才行……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event117-10-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"明日香","body":"但是啊，RAS他們是你說的『不是這些團員就不行』\n這樣的人們嗎？　你之前說過吧？\n想要遇到，像Popipa一樣的團員","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event117-10-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"雖然一開始以為他們好像是很恐怖的人，\n但跟大家一起演奏之後，就非常地……該怎麼說呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event117-10-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"……嗯。\n想著如果能這樣持續的話就好了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event117-10-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":214}],"windowDisplayName":"明日香","body":"這樣啊，那我也算是放下一顆心了吧。\n但是啊，這樣的話你跟姊姊他們就會變成像是敵人的感覺耶？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":214,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":214,"voiceId":"event117-10-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"啊！　跟Roselia也是！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event117-10-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"